/**********************************************************************/
/* frame, notebook, tab                                               */
/*                                                                    */
/* NOTE:  Perl/Tk uses weird default color-combinations for notebooks */
/* which are counter-intuitive, contrary to other widget-groupings,   */
/* and downright ugly imho (tab bar and non-selected tabs background  */
/* to a blazing white and selected tab is base color, and tabs have   */
/* rounded top borders) (Tk tabs are always on top / GTK tabs can be  */
/* on any of the four sides).  Therefore I took liberty to redo the   */
/* styles slightly here while maintaining the general Tk-look as best */
/* as possible.  Feel free to alter as you see fit.                   */
/*                                                                    */
/* Most of the notebook stuff ideas came from "CDETHEME 1.3" (whereas */
/* the rest originiated with the "OneStepBack" theme,                 */
/* by Jean-Pierre Bucciol - see README file)                          */
/* CREDIT:  CDETHEME 1.3 / JOS@JOSVANRISWICK.COM:                     */
/* https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1231025                               */
/**********************************************************************/

